    "name": "三国诡影：黄天",
    "steam_appid": 3241190,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras/1d733996c048709089cf3c7a1793fbec.avif?t=1730601264\" width=560 height=237 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras/a07a195f959abc3f565a07e19689f28b.avif?t=1730601264\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras_big/a07a195f959abc3f565a07e19689f28b.avif?t=1730601264 width=800 height=392 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >公元189年，汉灵帝中平六年。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黄巾起义已经过去了五年，但东汉王朝仍然呈现出一片暮气，年仅34岁的皇帝病笃，不断出现灾异，雌鸡化雄、蝗灾、水灾……甚至有一条大白蛇出现在皇宫的大殿中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >许多人在传说，炎汉已经失去了天命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >彼时的曹操还是渴望安邦定国的热血青年，他曾经参加过与黄巾军主力的决战，但战后却失去了记忆，而且一直受着头风和幻觉的困扰。为了找回记忆，他开始调查洛阳周边与太平道有关联的神秘组织长生道，而他老师的女儿文姬也“兴趣使然”地加入。随着调查深入，长生道有关的一切愈发诡异起来……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另一方面，洛阳执金吾（负责洛阳治安的官员）的义子也进入长生道卧底，结识了少女王婵和许多长生道的人们，逐步挖掘出长生道和黄巾甚至和东汉王朝的秘密联系……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras/315cf234e2f56483017effce991a58fc.avif?t=1730601264\" width=560 height=237 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras/c48bcc06ec8f31da9dd232dd72be0969.avif?t=1730601264\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras_big/c48bcc06ec8f31da9dd232dd72be0969.avif?t=1730601264 width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【中式克苏鲁AVG】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拒绝模仿克系的表象，专注描绘符合东汉末年时代背景的中式克苏鲁，描述历史上有零星记载的诡异事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【双主角双线悬疑】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情丰富的文字冒险游戏。玩家将扮演曹操和李飞，探寻三国时期诡异事件的另一种可能。双主角双线叙事，在两人眼中同一事件可能完全不同，每个叙事线都有多结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【填补史料背后的诡影】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一个改编故事，我们的角色并不完全和历史中形象相同，但会基于大量史料架构一个诡异但可信的三国世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras/4b6523707eaba5c4a6034bcd5505e148.avif?t=1730601264\" width=560 height=237 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras/9715c45d25cdee6fdf1e1b99d1f2ea6c.avif?t=1730601264\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras_big/9715c45d25cdee6fdf1e1b99d1f2ea6c.avif?t=1730601264 width=800 height=504 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras/151272450614560d4242e2af8888dae3.avif?t=1730601264\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras_big/151272450614560d4242e2af8888dae3.avif?t=1730601264 width=800 height=504 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras/11e753da1393ef76c52b3ce705e8979e.avif?t=1730601264\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras_big/11e753da1393ef76c52b3ce705e8979e.avif?t=1730601264 width=800 height=504 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras/f1a0347857b94faab02e077e0d5e266a.avif?t=1730601264\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras_big/f1a0347857b94faab02e077e0d5e266a.avif?t=1730601264 width=800 height=504 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras/16938b7c0e51c766045ca803cdeb1ee4.avif?t=1730601264\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras_big/16938b7c0e51c766045ca803cdeb1ee4.avif?t=1730601264 width=800 height=504 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras/49c95aaac716dfc63f3575a0041556dc.avif?t=1730601264\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241190/extras_big/49c95aaac716dfc63f3575a0041556dc.avif?t=1730601264 width=800 height=504 /></span></p>",
